{"tid":778885,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為棄嬰沖足七日涼仍未「洗白」 檢查始知「乖孫」是黑人","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:30:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T15:36:04.000Z","uid":200776,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ecb59f12884eefd25a3833d9fb3a228129f5a0","tid":778885,"uid":200776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/122848_252939c55a3e5e8f8dd24a88301ce3da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F122848_252939c55a3e5e8f8dd24a88301ce3da.jpg&h=800d2356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】上海一名婆婆朱水寶18年前買菜時，發現草叢中一名身體黑黑棄嬰，婆婆將他帶回家，<span style=\"color: red;\">幫他一天洗三次澡，連洗七天還是感覺洗不乾淨，送醫檢查才知他有黑人血統。</span>經過多年相依為命，朱婆婆把他視如己出，下個月更送他上大學。<br />\n<br />\n朱婆婆當時發現乖孫時，他全身黑黑，像沾到髒東西一樣，結果洗了一個星期都沒能洗白，直到後來帶去醫院檢查，醫生告訴她男嬰是混血兒才恍然大悟，朱婆婆把他帶回家撫養，「既然我這只手托了他，我苦中苦，我要托到底，讓他能在中國好好過！」。<br />\n<br />\n育有兩兒一女的朱婆婆給他改名為朱軍龍，為了使朱軍龍像其他孩子一樣正常受教育，朱婆婆經過14年奮鬥，直到2014年，終於幫朱軍龍成功登記戶口。朱軍龍現已長大成人，並將要上大學，朱婆婆對此十分期待。<br />\n<br />\n對於已74歲朱婆婆來說，朱軍龍學費有點壓力，每年大約2萬元人民幣，雖然朱婆婆每月只有2000元人民幣，但她表示，無論如何都會好好照顧他，讓他在中國快樂地過一生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caf16832d3c19ee0dc305027bc794ebcee509df","tid":778885,"uid":30081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ee9f492c76964bfc7dda48329fa846417a7363","tid":778885,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13c8400f9d6c79b4fcead234775c382ee27b071","tid":778885,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaac75cd236d7e65a88211c24400e7f9fabec9e5","tid":778885,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed75cbeeaf808f35ef744ee98f9fa74a8654365","tid":778885,"uid":11840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"if you try black you never go back"},{"pid":"277022d46c6fea7505a1f2ec02192e035e9550f4","tid":778885,"uid":200837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T15:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}